message.content:
Monday:
Breakfast - Oatmeal with banana and blueberries topped with chia seeds.
Lunch - Quinoa salad with mixed vegetables, chickpeas, and a lemon-tahini dressing.
Dinner - Grilled chicken breast with roasted sweet potatoes and steamed broccoli.
Snack - Apple slices with peanut butter.

Tuesday:
Breakfast - Smoothie made with almond milk, spinach, banana, strawberries, and a scoop of protein powder.
Lunch - Lentil soup topped with fresh cilantro.
Dinner - Baked salmon with roasted asparagus and brown rice.
Snack - Carrot sticks with hummus.

Wednesday:
Breakfast - Scrambled eggs with spinach, tomatoes, and onions.
Lunch - Chickpea salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, olives, and a lemon-oregano dressing.
Dinner - Baked tofu with quinoa and roasted bell peppers.
Snack - Celery sticks with almond butter.

Thursday:
Breakfast - Blueberry smoothie bowl made with coconut milk, blueberries, chia seeds, and a drizzle of maple syrup.
Lunch - Lentil-vegetable stir fry served over brown rice.
Dinner - Grilled shrimp skewers with zucchini noodles and sauteed kale.
Snack - Sliced pear with a spoonful of sunflower seed butter.

Friday:
Breakfast - Avocado toast on gluten-free bread topped with hemp seeds, tomatoes, and red pepper flakes.
Lunch - Chickpea salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, olives, and a lemon-oregano dressing.
Dinner - Baked chicken breast with roasted Brussels sprouts and quinoa.
Snack - Cottage cheese with pineapple chunks.

Saturday:
Breakfast - Chia seed pudding made with almond milk, vanilla extract, maple syrup, and topped with blueberries and strawberries.
Lunch - Quinoa salad with mixed vegetables, chickpeas, and a lemon-tahini dressing.
Dinner - Grilled steak with roasted cauliflower and sweet potatoes.
Snack - Sliced apple with almond butter.

Sunday:
Breakfast - Scrambled eggs with spinach, tomatoes, and onions.
Lunch - Lentil soup topped with fresh cilantro.
Dinner - Baked salmon with roasted asparagus and brown rice.
Snack - Carrot sticks with hummus.
